{"image_id": "CHD_2016_page_100", "image_size": [1238, 1613], "ocr": [{"text": "CHURCH & DWIGHT CO., INC. AND SUBSIDIARIES", "bbox": [364.7, 140.2, 873.4, 161.0]}, {"text": "NOTES TO CONSOLIDATED FINANCIAL STATEMENTS—(Continued)", "bbox": [279.5, 177.7, 958.4, 198.5]}, {"text": "(In millions, except share and per share data)", "bbox": [417.3, 202.7, 820.6, 223.5]}, {"text": "Board are fully vested in their account balance. As of December 31, 2016, there were approximately", "bbox": [143.8, 252.9, 981.8, 273.8]}, {"text": "307 thousand shares of Common Stock from shares held as Treasury Stock in a rabbi trust to protect the interest", "bbox": [143.8, 277.9, 1079.0, 298.8]}, {"text": "of the directors’ deferred compensation plan participants in the event of a change of control.", "bbox": [143.8, 302.9, 913.4, 323.8]}, {"text": "12. Share Repurchases", "bbox": [143.8, 372.3, 345.8, 393.2]}, {"text": "On November 2, 2016, the Board authorized a new share repurchase program, under which the Company", "bbox": [185.5, 412.4, 1063.9, 433.2]}, {"text": "may repurchase up to $500 million in shares of Common Stock (the “2016 Share Repurchase Program”). The", "bbox": [143.8, 437.4, 1057.9, 458.2]}, {"text": "2016 Share Repurchase Program does not have an expiration and replaced the 2015 Share Repurchase Program.", "bbox": [143.8, 462.4, 1079.1, 483.2]}, {"text": "The Company also continued its evergreen share repurchase program, authorized by the Board on January 29,", "bbox": [143.8, 487.4, 1061.4, 508.2]}, {"text": "2014, under which the Company may repurchase, from time to time, Common Stock to reduce or eliminate", "bbox": [143.8, 512.4, 1039.3, 533.2]}, {"text": "dilution associated with issuances of Common Stock under the Company’s incentive plans.", "bbox": [143.8, 537.4, 905.6, 558.2]}, {"text": "In 2016, the Company purchased approximately 9.0 million shares of Common Stock for $400.0, of which", "bbox": [185.5, 592.1, 1055.8, 612.9]}, {"text": "$103.0 was purchased under the evergreen share repurchase program, $200.0 was purchased under the 2016 Share", "bbox": [143.8, 617.1, 1076.4, 637.9]}, {"text": "Repurchase Program, and $97.0 was purchased under the 2015 Share Repurchase Program. As a result of the", "bbox": [143.8, 642.1, 1032.8, 663.0]}, {"text": "Company’s purchases, there remained $300.0 under the 2016 Share Repurchase Program as of December 31, 2016.", "bbox": [143.8, 667.1, 1085.4, 688.0]}, {"text": "13. Accumulated Other Comprehensive Income (Loss)", "bbox": [143.8, 736.5, 626.9, 757.4]}, {"text": "Comprehensive income is defined as net income and other changes in stockholders’ equity from transactions", "bbox": [185.5, 776.5, 1093.4, 797.4]}, {"text": "and other events from sources other than stockholders.", "bbox": [143.8, 801.5, 599.4, 822.4]}, {"text": "The components of changes in accumulated other comprehensive income (“AOCI”) are as follows:", "bbox": [185.5, 856.2, 1013.2, 877.1]}, {"text": "Foreign", "bbox": [719.2, 922.3, 774.8, 939.0]}, {"text": "Currency", "bbox": [712.8, 939.0, 781.3, 955.6]}, {"text": "Adjustments", "bbox": [701.7, 955.6, 792.5, 972.3]}, {"text": "Defined", "bbox": [809.1, 922.3, 864.6, 939.0]}, {"text": "Benefit", "bbox": [811.4, 939.0, 862.3, 955.6]}, {"text": "Plans", "bbox": [817.4, 955.6, 856.3, 972.3]}, {"text": "Derivative", "bbox": [886.8, 939.0, 960.9, 955.6]}, {"text": "Agreements", "bbox": [881.3, 955.6, 966.5, 972.3]}, {"text": "Accumulated", "bbox": [991.4, 905.6, 1085.9, 922.3]}, {"text": "Other", "bbox": [1017.4, 922.3, 1060.0, 939.0]}, {"text": "Comprehensive", "bbox": [983.1, 939.0, 1094.3, 955.6]}, {"text": "Income (Loss)", "bbox": [988.4, 955.6, 1088.9, 972.3]}, {"text": "Balance December 31, 2013 . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [143.8, 985.4, 685.1, 1006.3]}, {"text": "$ 12.7", "bbox": [720.2, 985.4, 774.1, 1006.3]}, {"text": "$(13.0)", "bbox": [809.9, 985.4, 870.7, 1006.3]}, {"text": "$ 0.5", "bbox": [902.1, 985.4, 945.6, 1006.3]